  "title": "Body Therapist Reflexologist Supervisor / Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide foot and body reflexology treatments according to company standards</li>\n  <li>Supervise and guide therapists to ensure consistent service quality</li>\n  <li>Manage daily operations, including staff scheduling and customer service</li>\n  <li>Maintain hygiene, safety, and cleanliness of the workplace</li>\n  <li>Handle customer enquiries, feedback, and service recovery</li>\n  <li>Assist with stock checks, ordering of supplies, and basic administrative duties</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Relevant experience in reflexology or body therapy</li>\n  <li>Professional certification in massage/reflexology preferred</li>\n  <li>Strong leadership and communication skills</li>\n  <li>Able to supervise, train, and motivate staff</li>\n  <li>Customer-service oriented with a professional attitude</li>\n  <li>Able to work shifts, weekends, and public holidays</li>\n</ul>",
